    {
      "id": "PopularPost302900",
      "post_content": "Most of the time you'll want Reckless charge for early game (or I guess late game..) haste; flashback is enough and the total cost of both castings is one of this guy's buybacks.  \n  \nThat said, it may be better in an \\*off color\\* deck. Blue/red control may get the type of mana to use this to make a 2/2 a faster finisher while having the mana needed.   \n  \nStill, it feels like [Burst Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burst Lightning) or something is more the thing for that.",
      "posted_by": "blurrymadness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost302900\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Most of the time you'll want Reckless charge for early game (or I guess late game..) haste; flashback is enough and the total cost of both castings is one of this guy's buybacks.<br/><br/>That said, it may be better in an *off color* deck. Blue/red control may get the type of mana to use this to make a 2/2 a faster finisher while having the mana needed. <br/><br/>Still, it feels like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Burst Lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Burst Lightning\">Burst Lightning</a> or something is more the thing for that.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '302900'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy44651\">blurrymadness</span>\r\n                                (3/6/2013 7:53:55 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftC