    {
      "id": "PopularPost352815",
      "post_content": "With the release of the Heroic mechanic, this becomes more interesting. The sorcery speed is still a big hit, but paying 4 mana per turn to get a Heroic trigger and make your guy a bruiser is pretty good, depending on the Heroic trigger.   \n  \n[Favored Hoplite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Favored Hoplite), for example - once Heroic goes off it can't be blocked and killed, and +3/+0 on top of the +1/+1 counter every turn makes it a mean threat.",
      "posted_by": "Magnor_Criol",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost352815\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">With the release of the Heroic mechanic, this becomes more interesting. The sorcery speed is still a big hit, but paying 4 mana per turn to get a Heroic trigger and make your guy a bruiser is pretty good, depending on the Heroic trigger.  <br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Favored Hoplite\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Favored Hoplite\">Favored Hoplite</a>, for example - once Heroic goes off it can't be blocked and killed, and +3/+0 on top of the +1/+1 counter every turn makes it a mean threat.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '352815'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy50569\">Magnor_Criol</span>\r\n                                (11/27/2013 5:22:10 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src